FBIS4-12692 "drnes070_l_94011" FBIS-NES-94-070 Daily Report 12 Apr 1994 ISRAEL Arab Woman Fatally Shot by Israeli in West Bank Arab Woman Fatally Shot by Israeli in West Bank TA1204092794 Tel Aviv IDF Radio in Hebrew 0900 GMT 12 Apr 94 TA1204092794 Tel Aviv IDF Radio Hebrew BFN [Text] An Arab woman was fatally shot by an Israeli truck driver in the territories today. The incident occurred near the village of al-Jib, south of Ramallah. Our correspondent in the territories Golan Yokhpaz reports that the man was driving a Coca-Cola truck along the Pisgat Ze'ev road in the direction of al-Ram junction when local residents apparently threw stones at the truck. The driver fired several shots from his handgun, killing a local woman on the spot. The commander of the Judaea Region police reported that searches to find the driver are currently under way.
